"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?9/17/9491?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Esophageal cancer (The Basics)",
"     </a>",
"    </p>",
"    <p class=\"headingAnchor2\" id=\"H23444149\">",
"     <span class=\"h3\">",
